      \n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \n      \n              \u003cp\u003eVeteran Indian jewellery designer \u003ca href=\"https://www.sunitashekhawat.com/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSunita Shekhawat\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e is known for breathing new life into the ancient craft of Meenakari, an age-old art form of enamelling metal surfaces with vibrant colours, patterns, and designs. So when her eponymous brand’s new flagship store in Jaipur was under development, it was decided that it should also house a\u003cstrong\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/momh_india\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emuseum-gallery\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e dedicated to exploring, preserving, and celebrating the Meenakari craft. Going one step further, New Delhi-based multidisciplinary design practice \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.studiolotus.in/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eStudio Lotus\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e channelled Jaipur’s architectural legacy and traditional artistry throughout their design. \u003cstrong\u003eThe result is a jewel-like building of artisanal craftsmanship, showcasing meticulously crafted interior frescoes and a striking hand-carved sandstone facade that evocatively echoes the pink palette the city is known for.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/23_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/23_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" alt=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" title=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/23_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Ishita Sitwala.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/20_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/20_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1981\" alt=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" title=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/20_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Ishita Sitwala.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1870\" alt=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" title=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5B