 Sitwala.\" title=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/25_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Ishita Sitwala.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/26_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/26_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1995\" alt=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" title=\"Photography by Ishita Sitwala.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/26_sunita_shekhawat_flagship_store_museum_of_meenakari_heritage_ishita_sitwala_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Ishita Sitwala.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003csection\u003e\n    \u003csection\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.yatzer.com/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003ch2\u003eA Jewel of Heritage: Sunita Shekhawat’s Flagship Store and Meenakari Museum in Jaipur\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e of \u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n        \n     \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e  \n  \n      \n  \u003c/section\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n      \n  \n      \u003csection\u003e\n      \